        <heading>Local Levy and Collection of Taxes</heading>
        <section eId="sec_12_133">
          <num>12-133</num>
          <heading>Taxes of subdivisions of towns</heading>
          <content>
            <p>Sec. 12-133. Taxes of subdivisions of towns.School district, fire district and highway taxes or taxes of any other subdivision of any town shall be laid either on the assessment list of the town last before completed or on the assessment list next thereafter to be completed, provided, if the list next thereafter to be completed is used, such taxes shall not become due and payable until such list has been completed. Each such tax shall be payable within one year after it has been laid.
